data.description: Welcome to your new home in the heart of Kenansville located at 210 N Mrytle Drive! If you are seeking an investment opportunity or a primary home to add your finishing touches to, then this is the one! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house offers a comfortable and spacious living experience. The mobile home was manufactured in 2005 which includes vaulted ceilings with a large kitchen space! The kitchen does need to be upgraded, along with a new bathroom and floors. The roof is original to the mobile home age and includes a new HVAC system which was installed only one year ago. This property has a higher value once the updates are done, and instant equity waiting. Don't let this one pass you by, call today before it is too late. The property is fully fenced and over a half-acre of land. Outside, you'll find a spacious backyard, ideal for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply relaxing. Enjoy the enlarged front screened patio. The attached carport provides convenient parking and additional storage space. Located on N Myrtle Drive, this home offers access to the local restaurants and post office in Kenansville. There is NO HOA and flood zone is X, which means NO Flood Zone! The home is away from the hustle and bustle of city life, but only 30 minutes to Saint Cloud and your nearest Publix for groceries. Lake Marian is minutes away with some of the best fishing in the area! Don't miss the opportunity to make this lovely property your new home. Schedule a viewing today! Cash only or financing program with preferred lender available.
